{"tid":936633,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（又到聖誕）施永青：屌你老母","createTime":"2018-12-11T02:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T10:19:18.000Z","uid":116214,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8827c9ba4bd334908e0837163c4f6615d0960901","tid":936633,"uid":116214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDqFaCb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDqFaCb.png&h=759e1dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有Hard Feeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"87c3ca76873a27f099dd321147f1b08a06b15a1d","tid":936633,"uid":82450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"好記仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06ceaeb55dc654b8b0af04297ae1c1b215c6081","tid":936633,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"中意佢夠真. 做朋友一流"},{"pid":"644f6dc4e0d55ba1bff74aea4a4409e0e0878fb5","tid":936633,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"又一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c27afbaca4cf2944fdc3bee996d2a2290042b6","tid":936633,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"明明細個咁窮，發咗達就唔會幫返窮的香港人。<br />\n唉，中國人就係咁。"},{"pid":"a3dc10c7a54e83e2e17dc9d38f340fc1f00263f1","tid":936633,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /